After clicking on the model selection, you can see whether the model supports image recognition and the ability to control whether to start image recognition. 
After starting image recognition, the model will read the image content in the file link, and if the user question is less than 500 words, it will automatically parse the image in the user question.

max_histories_number_tip:
The maximum number of rounds of dialogue that the model can carry into memory. If the memory exceeds the model context, the system will force truncation. 
Therefore, even if 30 rounds of dialogue are configured, the actual number may not reach 30 rounds during operation.

show_top_p_tip:
An alternative method of temperature sampling, called Nucleus sampling, the model considers the results of tokens with TOP_P probability mass quality. 
Therefore, 0.1 means that only tokens containing the highest probability quality are considered. 
The default is 1.
